          "href": "https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Aaron_Beck"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "Aaron Beck was known for a great many things. One of them is",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "cognitive behavioral therapy",
          "marks": [
            "link-0"
          ]
        },
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "—a method he invented that’s changed (and possibly saved) thousands of lives.",
          "marks": []
        }
      ],
      "markDefs": [
        {
          "_key": "link-0",
          "_type": "link",
          "href": "https://www.nhs.uk/mental-health/talking-therapies-medicine-treatments/talking-therapies-and-counselling/cognitive-behavioural-therapy-cbt/how-it-works/"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "The gist of it is this: problems appear less complicated (and intimidating) when they're broken down into parts than when they are seen as an undivided whole.",
          "marks": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "You can overcome almost anything by breaking it down into manageable bits, and then focusing on amending the latter to overcome or improve the former.",
          "marks": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "Changing the way you act and feel by embracing new moods, mindsets, and habits.",
          "marks": []
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}